Dear Sir,
I think that Charles Dickens[1] is the greatest novelwriter of the 19 century, and that his works, impressed with the true Christian spirit, have done and will continue to do a great deal of good to mankind.
Yours truly
Leo Tolstoy.
3 Febr. 1904.
Милостивый государь,
Искренно ваш
Лев Толстой.
